  "description": "\nUsed as an intermediary authenication screen\n\n",
  "name": "Sign In Screen",
  "usage": "\nUsed as an intermediary authenication screen\n\n#### Markup Example\n```html\n <div class=\"sign-in-screen flex flex--middle flex--center\">\n\n   <div class=\"\n     sign-in-screen__box box box--border-none u-m-- u-small-m+\n     u-ph- u-pv+ u-small-ph+++ u-small-pv++ u-medium-pv+++\n     \">\n\n     <div aria-label=\"GE monogram logo.\" class=\"text-align--center u-small-mt- u-medium-mt0\">\n       <eds-icon\n         class=\"sign-in-screen__logo--large u-mb--\"\n         load-method=\"name\"\n         svg-style='{\"width.px\":\"100\",\"height.px\":\"100\",\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}'\n         filename=\"ico-gelogo-32\">\n       </eds-icon>\n       <eds-icon\n         class=\"sign-in-screen__logo--small\"\n         load-method=\"name\"\n         svg-style='{\"width.px\":\"72\",\"height.px\":\"72\",\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}'\n         filename=\"ico-gelogo-32\">\n       </eds-icon>\n     </div>\n\n         <form action=\"\" method=\"post\" class=\"u-small-ph++ u-medium-ph+++ u-pt-\">\n       <fieldset class=\"form__fieldset u-p0 u-m0\">\n           <legend class=\"sign-in-screen__legend text-align--center u-smallest-mb-- u-small-mb++\">Product Name</legend>\n           <div class=\"u-small-mb u-smallest-mb--- u-mt-\">\n             <label class=\"form__label form__label--bottom\" for=\"un\">User name</label>\n             <input class=\"textbox text-16\" type=\"text\" id=\"un\" required #usernameField />\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"u-smallest-pt- u-small-pt0 u-small-mb u-smallest-mb---\">\n             <label class=\"form__label form__label--bottom\" for=\"pw\">Password</label>\n             <div class=\"sign-in-screen__pos-r\">\n               <input class=\"textbox text-16 u-pr+\" [attr.type]=\"fieldTypePass\" id=\"pw\" required #passwordField />\n               <button (click)=\"fieldType($event)\" aria-controls=\"pw\" aria-label=\"Expose password.\" class=\"button button--icon button--icon-transparent sign-in-screen__toggle-password\" id=\"toggle-password\" type=\"button\">\n                 <eds-icon\n                   *ngIf=\"fieldTypePass === 'password'\"\n                   load-method=\"name\"\n                   svg-style='{\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}'\n                   filename=\"ico-preview-16\">\n                 </eds-icon>\n\n                 <eds-icon\n                   *ngIf=\"fieldTypePass === 'text'\"\n                   load-method=\"name\"\n                   svg-style='{\"fill\":\"currentColor\"}'\n                   filename=\"ico-preview-hide-16\">\n                 </eds-icon>\n               </button>\n             </div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"u-smallest-pt- u-small-pt0 u-small-mb u-smallest-mb---\">\n             <label class=\"checkbox u-mb0\" for=\"remember01\">\n                 <input class=\"checkbox__input\" id=\"remember01\" type=\"checkbox\">\n                 <span class=\"checkbox__label\">Remember me</span>\n             </label>\n           </div>\n           <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button flex--center u--1/1 u-smallest-mt- u-small-mt0 u-smallest-mb--- u-small-mb--\">Sign in</button>\n       </fieldset>\n     </form>\n\n     <div class=\"u-pt- text-14 text-align--center u-small-ph++ u-medium-ph+++\">\n         <a href=\"#!\">Forgot password?</a>\n         <div class=\"u-pb-- u-smallest-pt--- u-small-pt+\"><hr class=\"sign-in-screen__hr u-smallest-mt- u-small-mt0\"/></div>\n         Don't have an account? <a href=\"#!\" class=\"u-ml---\">Register</a>\n     </div>\n </div>\n\n</div>\n```\n",
  "version": "1.1.4",
  "browsers": "chrome, safari, firefox, ie11, edge"
}